[{"Id": 1013854, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Through a valid chain of authority, Imam Kazim (a) is reported to have asked Ibrahim ibn Abil Ballad, “What do you say when you visit Husain (a)?” The man answered: I say the following words. The Imam (a) commented, Yes, this is accurate…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Imam Kazim (a) ne Ibrahim Ibne Abil Ballad se poocha, Jab tum Imam Husain (a) ki ziyarat par jaate ho to tum kya kehte to? Us shakhs ne is alfaaz ko dauraaya. Imam (a) ne kaha, Yeh bilkul sahih hai…", "UrduDescription": "معتبر سند سے نقل ہوا ہے کہ امام موسیٰ کاظم ؑنے ابراہیم ابن ابی البلاد سے فرمایا : جب تم امام حسینؑ کی زیارت کو جاتے ہو تو وہاں کیا پڑھتے ہو؟ اس نے کہا : میں یہ کہا کرتا ہوں۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "Ara